State summary info

urban_rural_pop.Rd

Census info for the 50 US states plus DC.

urban_rural_pop

Format

A tibble with 51 observations on the following 5 variables.

state

US state.

urban_in

a numeric vector

urban_out

a numeric vector

rural_farm

a numeric vector

rural_nonfarm

a numeric vector

Source

US census.

Examples


urban_rural_pop
